	short and to-the-point response.\n\nKeep the cover page separate from the a
	ssignment content. It should include your name and identify the assignment.
	 Place the references on a separate page\, unless in-text references are us
	ed. \n\nThe file you upload must include your first or last name in the fil
	ename. Failure to do so will result in a 3-POINT PENALTY. This requirement 
