UID:96949@moodle.humphreys.edu
SUMMARY:Assignment #3 (Wk4: Infographic) is due
DESCRIPTION:This assignment requires you to create a one-page Infographic w
	ith the content described below. \n\nInfographics can be created easily and
	 for free. The following are some websites that can be used for creating In
	fographics.\n\nhttps://www.canva.com/ [1]\n\nhttps://piktochart.com/pricing
	/education/ [2]\n\nhttps://www.hubspot.com/infographic-templates [3]\n\nOve
	r the past two weeks\, you have explored various aspects of privacy. In thi
	s assignment\, you will create an infographic.\n\n \n\nAssume you are the n
	ew IT/Data Manager for a large manufacturing company. Recent data breaches 
	have compromised customer information\, and you have been tasked with devel
	oping a one-page infographic to be displayed across employee workspaces.\n\
	n \n\nThe infographic should be visually engaging\, easy to understand\, an
	d capture employee attention. It must include:\n\n	* A definition of “priva
	cy” in the context of customer/consumer data\n	* The level of privacy custo
	mers should expect when doing business with your organization\n	* THREE spe
	cific strategies employees must follow to protect customer data from breach
	es\, misuse\, or carelessness\n\n Adhere to the following submission requir
	ements:\n\n	* Infograph must be one-page\n	* Include at least two credible 
	references (course materials are acceptable)\; provide a reference page (ma
	y be on page two)\n	* Submissions will be evaluated based on content\, visu
	al appeal\, and strength of message\n\n\n\nLinks:\n------\n[1] https://www.
	canva.com/\n[2] https://piktochart.com/pricing/education/\n[3] https://www.
	hubspot.com/infographic-templates\n
	
