UID:96952@moodle.humphreys.edu
SUMMARY:Assignment #5 (Wk7: eMail) is due
DESCRIPTION:ASSIGNMENT\n\nThe workplace is evolving rapidly\, with increasi
	ng reliance on robots and artificial intelligence (AI). This shift has crea
	ted concern among employees about potential job loss.\n\nAs the Human Resou
	rces Manager\, you have been asked to draft a 1–2 page email to all employe
	es addressing these concerns. Your email should explain:\n\n	* What are “ro
	bots”?\n	* What is “artificial intelligence”?\n	* How increased use of robo
	ts and AI has contributed to job displacement\n	* How the nature of work is
	 expected to change in the coming years\n	* What employees can do to remain
	 effective and relevant in this environment\n\nSUBMISSION REQUIREMENTS\n\n	
	* Support your analysis with at least 2 references\n	* Be POSITIVE AND UPLI
	FTING in your email\n	* Email length should be 1-2 pages long\n\n
	
